{"tid":954581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(學生有圖)「喜茶」最貴$49一杯 學生無食lunch呆等幾粒鐘：有啲後悔","createTime":"2018-12-24T16:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T18:48:19.000Z","uid":16697,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a27ab46a00cb8ff8023b48965f004a53c17baf0","tid":954581,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181224/59066546?fbclid=IwAR3_o4GMMQ258vXc0PrfiN7pH4y9_3rJ2CA2-QWXiagmYeOnmDSdOUeKB5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59066546%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3_o4GMMQ258vXc0PrfiN7pH4y9_3rJ2CA2-QWXiagmYeOnmDSdOUeKB5s&d=nqjC3m2unEyQmqiy%2FoOF5P1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dc171e14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F59066546%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3_o4GMMQ258vXc0PrfiN7pH4y9_3rJ2CA2-QWXiagmYeOnmDSdOUeKB5s&h=0f103abb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181224/59066546?fbclid=IwAR3_o4GMMQ258vXc0PrfiN7pH4y9_3rJ2CA2-QWXiagmYeOnmDSdOUeKB5s</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181224/large/1545645944_3bdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181224%2Flarge%2F1545645944_3bdb.jpg&h=42da0329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港「喜茶」首間分店在沙田開幕，數百人打蛇餅排隊「朝聖」，該店售價最貴的飲品是「芝芝莓果」及「多肉莓莓」，兩款均售49元一杯，最平的飲品是純茶類的「冷萃知秋」，售18元一杯。其他產品包括特色雪糕，最平的是「茶王雪糕」，售12元。<br />\n<br />\n大學生羅小姐和仼先生今早9時45分來到，最終下午1點45分多，歷時4個小時，才成功購得3杯飲品。仼生指因為考完試，來到買杯飲品當慶祝，又認為味道與內地分別不大。他又提到，香港製作時間較久，店方亦曾「漏單」，等了約1小時才能拿到飲品。<br />\n中學生黃同學等逾4個小時才成功購得飲品，她笑言𣎴太值得，稱香港的價錢較內地貴，直言下次會回內地買。她又指香港製作程序較內地慢，建議應如內地分店，有手機提示領取飲品的服務，以減少等待時間。另一學生廖同學表示，沒有吃午餐，等了數小時「有啲後悔」，但排了如此長時間，也只好等下去。大學生李小姐與2名朋友約11時來到排隊，因為「無嘢做」所以來買杯飲品「打卡」，她也笑言要排隊這樣久，不太值得。<br />\n<br />\n據喜茶官網簡介，喜茶於2012年，在廣東江門一條小巷起家，只有200多平方呎的店舖，原名為「皇茶」，其後因商標問題改名為「喜茶」。現時「喜茶」在內地多個省份擁有75間「直營店」，當中廣州有21間，深圳有15間，上海有5間，北京亦有2間，整體營業額已達過億元人民幣，其90後創辦人聶雲宸曾指「沒有一間店虧損，所有店是盈利的。」"},{"pid":"76c343d274b20c64bca3ddf8afed5059d772772d","tid":954581,"uid":135767,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b47836493b3ac543dc33088181b9502c7624fd42","tid":954581,"uid":117967,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"見住成班傻閪排住等飲屎水就不期然暗爽"},{"pid":"06fb5a2eb373fc64659073c38ae261ec884d1c42","tid":954581,"uid":74990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"成班都痴線"},{"pid":"18354618a236f7624eefa7bf6dbd41f0426796fa","tid":954581,"uid":153144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:33:37.000Z","msg":"條女隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1348f25b47de9145b7d3b935a93334b976c624e0","tid":954581,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"估到會排好耐, 因為放假, 加上買一送一. <br />\n班友重唔狗衝咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28108b09199198df8764a8dc6c18bb4335e7997e","tid":954581,"uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1348f25b47de9145b7d3b935a93334b976c624e0","tid":954581,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"估到會排好耐, 因為放假, 加上買一送一. <br />\n班友重唔狗衝咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:01:29.000Z","msg":"一送一後你估仲駛唔駛排"},{"pid":"13302cd97ed4539ea9acab83bfdc97282e012239","tid":954581,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:08:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得係慢慢沖 , 拖慢來做. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8bf04d5644434125952e0b30631cdb612d8182","tid":954581,"uid":21602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"大陸喜茶成日請人假排隊有糧出<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n刺激D打卡港豬鎊水排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2be7e2f041041f00059948e4c56e122c60ebbd","tid":954581,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那野都排隊"},{"pid":"9eae37dbd796a00832c4159379643d7cf24313e3","tid":954581,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsJpXJR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsJpXJR.gif&h=d7ffd7a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69c6704de9e2ddaf407a3e9aa0539e821dec85f5","tid":954581,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:23:37.000Z","msg":"冇人逼你買"},{"pid":"d23b953d01234d5820da9e242b40c83beeaa681c","tid":954581,"uid":21378,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8b2be7e2f041041f00059948e4c56e122c60ebbd","tid":954581,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那野都排隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"公開秘密<br />\nsearch <br />\n喜茶 假排隊<br />\n<br />\n有間叫飽師傅, 已經出晒名. <br />\n排隊黨. 已經係一個行業. <br />\n請人排7日 , 羊群心理, 有成效. 唔洗再放太多人. <br />\n自然有班人會排隊. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以點解 某些分店係好少人. 唔洗排隊, 係有原因. <br />\n唔係因為非旺區, 只係投資少咗. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5026fd5eb224b15ccfe84dcaefa6c02793c58dc","tid":954581,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"排隊俾錢買垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}